If i want to break a paragraph entered by user, into substrings separated by spaces i will use split function 

For example:-
String line = "apple banana cherry";
String[] fruits = line.split(" ");  // ["apple", "banana", "cherry"]


for ultimate separation :-
String text = "hello, world!java;python:go   rust";
String[] words = text.split("[\\s,.;:!?]+");
// Result: ["hello", "world", "java", "python", "go", "rust"]
this separates on basis of every punctuations marks


"word1,,,word2...word3   word4".split("[\\s,.;:!?]+")
// ["word1", "word2", "word3", "word4"]
// Note: Multiple delimiters treated as one split poin
